Task 1 : Student Marksheet  Using Operator 

Task assigned : 
1. Add variable with first and last name
2. create any five subject and get marks as input
3. find total marks and get out percentage
4. if percentage satisfy criteria then student will pass otheer wise fail ( criteria is 60 % , can put any criteria if anyone ants to changed the criteria)

-----------------XXXX-----------------

Code  :  

first_name = str(input("Enter the First Name : "))
last_name = str(input("Enter the Last Name : "))

maths  = float(input("Please enter your Maths marks : ")) 

science = float(input("Please enter your science marks : "))

English  = float(input("Please enter your English marks : "))

Python  = float(input("Please enter your Python marks : "))

SQl  = float(input("Please enter your SQl marks : "))


total_marks = maths + science + English + Python + SQl

percentage = ( total_marks / 500 ) * 100   # 500 for 5 subject each subject consist of 100 marks

grade = [ " Fail " , "Pass"]

grade_index = (percentage > 60)  # 0/ 1


final_grade = grade[grade_index]  # grade[0] / grade[1]

print(" Marksheet Report of the Student \n ")
print("Name of the Student",first_name,last_name)



print("subjects\n","Maths : ",maths , "\n" ,"Science : ", science , "\n" , "English : ",English , "\n","Python : ", Python,"\n", "SQL : ",SQl )

print("Percentage of the student : ",percentage)

print("Result of the student : ",final_grade)

-----------------XXXX-----------------

